name: JCX Blend
description:
Anime style focused blend. Generates images somewhere between 2d and 2.5d, but it is capable of both with the right prompts.

This blend has been made by merging a few different anime and 2/2.5d models to various degrees.

Its strength lies in fantasy but it is also capable of more realistic or futuristic settings.

Highly recommended to use the following negative textual inversion:

  • badhandv4

  • bad-artist

  • bad-artist-anime

  • bad_prompt_version2

VAE has been baked in.

The examples were made by a combination of txt2img and img2img, inpainting and upscaling techniques.

Model tends to be slightly perverted when it comes to female characters. It is highly capable of nsfw. Keep nsfw tags in the negative prompt to prevent.
